java/ch_qos_reload4j/reload4j/SocketNodeTest.java`\n\nThe new test exercises `org.apache.log4j.net.SocketNode.run(...)` by:\n\n- Opening a loopback socket pair.\n- Sending a serialized `LoggingEvent` through an `ObjectOutputStream`.\n- Running `SocketNode` against the accepted socket.\n- Verifying the deserialized event is dispatched to the repository logger’s appender.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d3c8d78e21999880169f50ddc271481a299db72d21bb8a2ca\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 454, "output": 649, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23119, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777667537778, "responseId": "resp_0d3c8d78e21999880169f50dd23cbc81a297b2e31a1c72645e"}, "toolResults": []}
